    "description": "Are you a skilled Manufacturing Engineer looking for your next big career move? Microtek International in Ahmedabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Microtek International:\nMicrotek International is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Microtek International!",
